                <head>302. Editorial Note</head>
                <p>On November 4, the National Security Council approved <gloss target="#t_NSC1"
                        >NSC</gloss> 5910/1, “U.S. Policy on France,” which contained a section on
                    “The Algerian Problem.” Paragraph 42c defined policy guidance on Algeria. <gloss
                        target="#t_NSC1">NSC</gloss> 5910/1 is scheduled for publication in <ref
                        target="frus1958-60v07p1">volume VII</ref>.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
